  <steps>
    <step order="1">Read SpaarkeAi `main.tsx` and locate the existing `setDefaultWorkspaceRenderer` call.</step>
    <step order="2">Read `loadSpaarkeAiNotificationContext.ts` to confirm signature matches the factory option from task 001.</step>
    <step order="3">Add the factory invocation with `loadNotificationContext: loadSpaarkeAiNotificationContext` alongside the existing renderer setup.</step>
    <step order="4">Verify nothing else in `main.tsx` shadows or short-circuits the registration.</step>
    <step order="5">Run `npm run build` on `src/solutions/SpaarkeAi/` and confirm no type or build errors.</step>
    <step order="6">Update TASK-INDEX.md: change task 002 status from 🔲 to ✅.</step>
